### ==========================================================================
### BildyApp API — Ficheros .http de ejemplo
### Usable con: VS Code REST Client, IntelliJ HTTP Client, etc.
### ==========================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = Bearer TU_ACCESS_TOKEN_AQUI
@refreshToken = TU_REFRESH_TOKEN_AQUI

### ─── Health ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ==========================================================================
### USER — Registro, Login, Onboarding
### ==========================================================================

### Registro de usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "Segura123!"
}

###

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@ejemplo.com",
  "password": "Segura123!"
}

###

### Verificar email (requiere token)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/user/validation
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "123456"
}

###

### Completar datos personales (onboarding)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/user/register
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hugo",
  "lastName": "Olza",
  "nif": "12345678A",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle Mayor",
    "number": "10",
    "postal": "28001",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  }
}

###

### Crear/actualizar compañía
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/user/company
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isFreelance": false,
  "name": "Mi Empresa SL",
  "cif": "B12345678",
  "address": {
    "street": "Calle Empresa",
    "number": "5",
    "postal": "28002",
    "city": "Madrid",
    "province": "Madrid"
  }
}

###

### Obtener perfil del usuario autenticado
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Refresh token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/logout
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Eliminar cuenta (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/user?soft=true
Authorization: {{token}}

###

### Eliminar cuenta (hard delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/user
Authorization: {{token}}
